high_descs: Walk around the table to face the opposite side.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Walk around the table to face the head of lettuce on the left.
Cut the head of lettuce into slices.
Step back to face the right side of the table.
Place the knife on the right side of the table.
Look left to face the sliced lettuce on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
walk around the table to the left and turn left to face the shelves in the corner on the wall.
Place the slice of lettuce in the bowl on the shelf.
Pick up the bowl with a lettuce slice in it on the shelf.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Put the bowl with a lettuce slice in it into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a slice of lettuce in a bowl and store it in the fridge.

Turn around towards the table
Put knife on the table
Get closer to the table
Grab a slice of the lettuce from the table

Put the lettuce slice in the bowl on the shelf
Grab the bowl from the shelf
Walk with the bowl towards the fridge
Put the bowl in the fridge

Pick up the butter knife from the kitchen island
Walk around to the other side of the kitchen island
Cut the left most lettuce on the island with the knife

Put the knife on the kitchen island just behind the salt shaker
Walk up to the kitchen island
pick up a piece of lettuce from the kitchen island
Turn left and walk around the kitchen island to the wooden shelf by the window
